{"id": "1311176228002201631", "channel_id": "1310906343972147280", "type": 19, "author_id": "1139928180254326927", "author_name": "rock1234_47882", "author_bot": false, "content": "那个艾尔瓦满分的配队是希洛羊妈诺蒂拉艾尔瓦，主旨是通过面具反复开超限叠爆伤以及攒0费盾（解封印），在臭脚回合集中爆发", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T03:46:13.232000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["989203680383344701"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1311041417040236635", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1310906343972147280", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "希望加強一下艾爾瓦", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
